title: Distribution of gross domestic product ( GDP ) across economic sectors Cuba 2018
summary: In general Share of GDP has stayed the same over the Year.
Share of GDP is slightly decreasing from 2011 to 2012, and lastly roughly constant from 2012 to 2013.
Maximum Share of GDP, about 73.01 was reported at Year 2011
Minimum Share of GDP about 71.66 was reached at Year 2012
